  "time_ut": 1658036291,
  "original_lang": "si",
  "original_title": "\u0da7\u0dd2\u0dba\u0dd1\u0db1\u0dca\u0dc2\u0ddd-3 \u0db7\u0dcf\u0dab\u0dca\u0da9 \u0db4\u0dca\u200d\u0dbb\u0dc0\u0dcf\u0dc4\u0db1 \u0dba\u0dcf\u0db1\u0dba \u0dba\u0dc5\u0dd2 \u0d9c\u0db8\u0db1\u0d9a\u0da7 \u0dc3\u0dd6\u0daf\u0dcf\u0db1\u0db8\u0dca",
  "text_idx": {
    "en": {
      "title": "The Tianzhou-3 cargo plane is ready to go again",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "The Tianzhou-3 cargo spacecraft has fully separated from the space station core module and is preparing to return to Earth.",
        "According to the Chinese Manned Space Engineering Office (CMSEO), the separation took place after the completion of all assigned space station assembly tasks."
      ],
